{"tid":2081359,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實要辨識分化L好簡單","createTime":"2020-06-27T07:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T09:37:14.000Z","uid":199431,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e3426c4e656b07c295b685ddcf6d2d8bfefe6fa6","tid":2081359,"uid":199431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:08:17.000Z","msg":"上年到而家愈來愈多五毛/藍屍/PR/分化L<br />\n三日唔埋兩日就開po批鬥特定target <br />\n由餐廳到youtuber,再到議員都有人批鬥<br />\n基本上係黃圈就有人鬧<br />\n再由佢地咁落去始終唔係辦法<br />\n<br />\n但係點先分到<span style=\"color: gold;\">有利黃圈可持續發展嘅意見</span>同<span style=\"color: navy;\">分化po</span>？<br />\n<br />\n關鍵就在於有冇提及<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃圈入面嘅可替代選擇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n舉例而言：<br />\n如果你覺得龍門難食，咁喺批評龍門嘅同時，就應該講埋有啲咩可替代龍門嘅黃店，例如喺龍門附近嘅水門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有人齋鬧黃店又唔講下有咩alternatives可以揀/應該點改善，咁對黃圈冇幫助，只係鼓吹分化批鬥風氣<br />\n<br />\n成效：<br />\n咁做就可以<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">令黃圈入面嘅消費力留翻入黃圈</span></span>入面，而唔會因為揾唔到選擇而外流<br />\n<br />\n反駁：<br />\n如果你話揾唔到可替代選擇（其實而家揾黃店好方便，冇咩可能揾唔到），咁就即係話得番兩條路<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">含淚繼續食</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">脫離黃色消費圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n黃色消費圈重點係唔想資敵，將資源從紅圈藍圈抽出嚟，呢個原則先係黃色生活圈嘅核心，所以當冇其他選擇時就只有含淚<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">含淚從來都唔係選擇，而係別無選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5a0f5cd152c4fe30f03ae107b40df3a347db8486","tid":2081359,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93189fd8943e24e56e9692735b80411796bc8986","tid":2081359,"uid":199431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b411c0854dddd9e05b9e75e3d99fcfd933a2cf49","tid":2081359,"uid":199431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:13:45.000Z","msg":"Self push"},{"pid":"ba045d0dee77a730d009c32c48c382d475a81e9e","tid":2081359,"uid":199431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"dabb7221f2c63a2dd57122b712b4a826e4b08ddb","tid":2081359,"uid":199431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:27:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5bb7c822b0fead1fc2e535a40f0b8d6563c4f1f","tid":2081359,"uid":199431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61b8ee2a502deea579213f99eb9edab3746e6a7d","tid":2081359,"uid":199431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"542071c5909c86553cbd645c54e1768035e0a7d8","tid":2081359,"uid":199431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3dd8c845c96aa032d73d3f4ffd23de6671b30d1b","tid":2081359,"uid":199431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3d9e5d9f286956cb568a789a1ff880aa51063d80","tid":2081359,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10d0dd530720d9e37b2bbe470b01c6bad423d74","tid":2081359,"uid":196538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:08:40.000Z","msg":"推，淨係批評真係知幫助"},{"pid":"ea68f9d92cc89ccfd3457863024fa1a25cefbf1a","tid":2081359,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46b9ffb2858